data.description: Great location for a farm or a family compound! Welcome to this 63.08 acre lot in Danielsville. Zoned agricultural, there is a house on the property built in 1978 that needs some work, and there is also a chicken house that could easily be refurbished. The possibilities are endless on this property! Schedule a showing today to see if this property could be your next adventure!
